      (17 U.S.C.), specifically including but not limited to §§ 101–122 (Subject Matter and Scope of Copyright),
      §§ 201–205 (Copyright Ownership and Transfer), §§ 301–305 (Duration of Copyright), §§ 401–412 (Copyright
      Notice, Deposit, and Registration), and §§ 501–513 (Copyright Infringement and Remedies), as well as all
